  <Method>
    <Step image="">In a large sauté pan, sauté onions and garlic in olive oil until well caramelized. </Step>
    <Step image="">Add tomatoes, tomato paste, water, wine, clam juice, parsley and herbs, salt and pepper. </Step>
    <Step image=""> Bring to a boil, reduce to simmer and cook for 10 minutes.</Step>
    <Step image="">Add clams/mussels and fish, cook, covered,  for 5 more minutes.</Step>
    <Step image="">Add crab legs and shrimp, cook until shimp turn pink.  Discard any clams/mussels whose shells remain closed</Step>
    <Step image="">Serve with hard crusty sourdough bread. </Step>
  </Method>
